{"tid":1698950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【又係元朗】青朗公路寶馬撞工程車工人分屍亡 司機涉酒駕被捕","createTime":"2019-11-08T00:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:05:30.000Z","uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"af9a3f7a8bac6da97eca798fadaabb704f3ca7db","tid":1698950,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191108/60243003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60243003&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=3f3ae37f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60243003&h=24844bf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191108/60243003</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗青朗公路發生致命車禍，凌晨4時，一輛掛中港牌的寶馬SUV多用途車輛，沿路往元朗方向行駛，至大欖隧道收費亭不遠處失控，撞向路中一輛工程車，一名修路工人閃避不及慘被撞倒，夾在工程車與寶馬之間，攔腰斷開兩截當場死亡。寶馬司機接受酒精呼氣測試，證實度數超標，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕。<br />\n<br />\n車禍現場距離大欖隧道約200米，慢線進行舖瀝青工程，工人封慢線及中線，而工程車停在中線。事發時舖瀝青工程已完成，工人準備髹油畫分隔線。肇事寶馬沿快線駛至，突然失控越過中線，撞向該名35歲工人，將他推前一個車位，壓向前面的工程車，夾在兩車之間，上下身劏開兩截。"},{"pid":"b141d620cf9d1ecd1b9a36f61a2f327735b147f0","tid":1698950,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:36:01.000Z","msg":"消防員及救護員到場救援，將被困工人救出，證實他已經死亡。寶馬車頭亦嚴重損毀，25歲司機受傷，現場敷治後拒絕送院。警方封鎖現場調查。寶馬司機酒精呼氣測試30多度，返警署吹大機仍超標，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕。"},{"pid":"31f043bbe1ad0e2f9c31da30ce4cdc5a29f3a123","tid":1698950,"uid":273157,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:37:00.000Z","msg":"呢d仆街判刑一定輕過義士"},{"pid":"0454679c8965e6116a242468bc583cc0a251c388","tid":1698950,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"攔腰斷開兩截當場死亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe26c5464c66006e0ea9bd7116dfa4029975c22","tid":1698950,"uid":22637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:43:17.000Z","msg":"中港牌?<br />\n應該判1年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd5e7ff27a8bba13764d7a89a99c5b71b69d0a4","tid":1698950,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"撞死人不嬲判得好輕 見親都頂多4、5年貨仔<br />\n點解啲人成日話撞死人好過謀殺就係咁解<br />\n亦都解釋咗點解何妖單嘢差佬要告謀殺，而721黑幫頂多告暴動，一係揸刀嘅轉頭放咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74861158b051b2781b03f4cfa0351bee027af1f9","tid":1698950,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0454679c8965e6116a242468bc583cc0a251c388","tid":1698950,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"攔腰斷開兩截當場死亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"咁死法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f860cf6f804ce736b2699f1bb0452a96e42474","tid":1698950,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31f043bbe1ad0e2f9c31da30ce4cdc5a29f3a123","tid":1698950,"uid":273157,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:37:00.000Z","msg":"呢d仆街判刑一定輕過義士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"仲要支港牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再輕啲都等"},{"pid":"32e1f1155eaef70c54b418f41e6b6f76b3876902","tid":1698950,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"法官會唔會相信被告深感悔意，不會重犯，判社會服務令100小時？"},{"pid":"9a5ab683a00676d2bca2dbc4b7932b9657093dbb","